                            <div class="FaqModule" data-module  data-module-header-position="side">
    
    <a class="AnchorLink" href="#faqs" id="faqs" name="faqs"></a>



    <div class="ModuleHeader">
        <div class="ModuleHeader-container">
            
                <div class="ModuleHeader-title">FAQs</div>
            
            
                <div class="ModuleHeader-description">Common questions about protecting food production operations from cyber threats and implementing effective OT security programs.</div>
            
            
                

            
        </div>
    </div>



    <div class="FaqModule-container">
        <div class="FaqModule-items"><bsp-accordion class="FaqQuestion">
    <button class="FaqQuestion-header" data-accordion-header type="button" aria-expanded="false">
            <div class="FaqQuestion-title">
                How does anonymous sharing protect my organization?
                <span class="iconPlus" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor"><path d="M224,128a8,8,0,0,1-8,8H136v80a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V136H40a8,8,0,0,1,0-16h80V40a8,8,0,0,1,16,0v80h80A8,8,0,0,1,224,128Z"/></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="iconMinus" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor"><path d="M224,128a8,8,0,0,1-8,8H40a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H216A8,8,0,0,1,224,128Z"/></svg>
                </span>
            </div></button>
    <div class="FaqQuestion-answer" data-accordion-body>
        <div class="FaqQuestion-answerWrapper">
            <div class="RichTextBody"><p>Neighborhood Keeper strips identifying information while preserving threat intelligence value. Your data contributions remain completely anonymous while you benefit from community insights.</p></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</bsp-accordion>
<bsp-accordion class="FaqQuestion">
    <button class="FaqQuestion-header" data-accordion-header type="button" aria-expanded="false">
            <div class="FaqQuestion-title">
                What types of organizations can participate?
                <span class="iconPlus" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor"><path d="M224,128a8,8,0,0,1-8,8H136v80a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V136H40a8,8,0,0,1,0-16h80V40a8,8,0,0,1,16,0v80h80A8,8,0,0,1,224,128Z"/></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="iconMinus" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor"><path d="M224,128a8,8,0,0,1-8,8H40a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H216A8,8,0,0,1,224,128Z"/></svg>
                </span>
            </div></button>
    <div class="FaqQuestion-answer" data-accordion-body>
        <div class="FaqQuestion-answerWrapper">
            <div class="RichTextBody"><p>Any Dragos Platform customer, from small utilities, municipalities, to the largest commercial companies. It’s available to all who want to simplify their operation and gain network wide insights.</p></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</bsp-accordion>
<bsp-accordion class="FaqQuestion">
    <button class="FaqQuestion-header" data-accordion-header type="button" aria-expanded="false">
            <div class="FaqQuestion-title">
                How do I know my data is protected?
                <span class="iconPlus" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor"><path d="M224,128a8,8,0,0,1-8,8H136v80a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V136H40a8,8,0,0,1,0-16h80V40a8,8,0,0,1,16,0v80h80A8,8,0,0,1,224,128Z"/></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="iconMinus" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor"><path d="M224,128a8,8,0,0,1-8,8H40a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H216A8,8,0,0,1,224,128Z"/></svg>
                </span>
            </div></button>
    <div class="FaqQuestion-answer" data-accordion-body>
        <div class="FaqQuestion-answerWrapper">
            <div class="RichTextBody"><p>Neighborhood Keeper uses a double anonymization approach. First, any organization specific data (IP ranges, host names, etc.) are removed from the data exchange. Second, we use strong certificates to secure the data link, but there is no organization mapped to the certificate – we don’t know who you are, just that you have a Dragos Platform!</p></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</bsp-accordion>
<bsp-accordion class="FaqQuestion">
    <button class="FaqQuestion-header" data-accordion-header type="button" aria-expanded="false">
            <div class="FaqQuestion-title">
                Is there a cost to participate in Neighborhood Keeper?
                <span class="iconPlus" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor"><path d="M224,128a8,8,0,0,1-8,8H136v80a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V136H40a8,8,0,0,1,0-16h80V40a8,8,0,0,1,16,0v80h80A8,8,0,0,1,224,128Z"/></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="iconMinus" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor"><path d="M224,128a8,8,0,0,1-8,8H40a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H216A8,8,0,0,1,224,128Z"/></svg>
                </span>
            </div></button>
    <div class="FaqQuestion-answer" data-accordion-body>
        <div class="FaqQuestion-answerWrapper">
            <div class="RichTextBody"><p>Neighborhood Keeper is completely free for participants.</p></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</bsp-accordion>
<bsp-accordion class="FaqQuestion">
    <button class="FaqQuestion-header" data-accordion-header type="button" aria-expanded="false">
            <div class="FaqQuestion-title">
                What technical requirements are needed to participate?
                <span class="iconPlus" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor"><path d="M224,128a8,8,0,0,1-8,8H136v80a8,8,0,0,1-16,0V136H40a8,8,0,0,1,0-16h80V40a8,8,0,0,1,16,0v80h80A8,8,0,0,1,224,128Z"/></svg>
                </span>
                <span class="iconMinus" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 256 256" fill="currentColor"><path d="M224,128a8,8,0,0,1-8,8H40a8,8,0,0,1,0-16H216A8,8,0,0,1,224,128Z"/></svg>
                </span>
            </div></button>
    <div class="FaqQuestion-answer" data-accordion-body>
        <div class="FaqQuestion-answerWrapper">
            <div class="RichTextBody"><p>Neighborhood Keeper requires Dragos Platform with a persistent, secure network connection to enable telemetry queries and distribute weekly Knowledge Packs.</p></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</bsp-accordion>
</div>
        

